00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome to Burme Transcript App

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:08,000
This is a subtitle editing application

3
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:12,000
You can upload your own video and SRT files

4
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:16,000
Click on any subtitle to edit it in real-time

5
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:20,000
Use the time offset slider to sync subtitles

6
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:24,000
Export your edited subtitles as SRT file

7
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:28,000
Use keyboard shortcuts for quick control

8
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:32,000
Space = Play/Pause, Arrow keys = Seek

9
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:36,000
Enjoy editing your subtitles!